comments: Wood (HOU) makes marginal contact to Gobert's (UTA) upper body underneath the basket and he is able to move through to gather the loose ball.

Conley (UTA) briefly places his hand to Porter Jr.'s (HOU) side while defending his drive in transition and marginal contact occurs. Both players engage in incidental foot to foot contact.
